faqsDetails.faq_title: What would my VIP experience Include?
faqsDetails.faq_content: Yes. You can give us feedback by reviewing the order you placed.

faqsDetails.faq_title: What is the duration of my memership?
faqsDetails.faq_content: You can apply Promo Code on Check Out page.

faqsDetails.faq_title: How can I avail this for more than one person?
faqsDetails.faq_content: You can cancel your order within 5 minutes of placing the order, provided the restaurant has not accepted the order. In any other case you may contact us through Live Chat.

faqsDetails.faq_title: How can I share this with my friend?
faqsDetails.faq_content: The duration of the refund process varies depending on the payment method you used. Also, depending on your bank it may take anywhere between 2-7 working days.
